  "description": "<p>ARE YOU LOOKING FOR A ROLE THAT REWARDS YOU?</p><p><u><strong>About Us</strong></u></p><p>Part of a regional outsource events & marketing company, currently located in South Asia. Where we work closely with clients in different sectors to provide sales and marketing solutions, increases market shares value and creating brand awareness.<br /></p><p><u><strong>The Environment</strong></u></p><p>You will be provided with a place that fosters innovation, fun and excellence.</p><p>You get the freedom to be around people with good vibes, have the time for development and traveling with the company.</p><p><u><strong>Recruiting</strong></u></p><p>Our client is looking out for potential candidate to join us as Marketing Trainee in their expansion plans.</p><p><strong>As long as you are:</strong></p><ul><li>FUN 🥳</li><li>Willing to Learn 🤓</li><li>A Team Player 👫</li><li>Competitive ⛹</li></ul><p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p><ul><li>No experience needed 🚫</li><li>Leadership and guidance 📚</li><li>Self development 🧑</li><li>Fast Track Career Grosth 🔝</li></ul>",
